commit.title: Consistently declare all first word of Gallina commands as reserved identifiers.
commit.message:
Consistently declare all first word of Gallina commands as reserved identifiers.

They are not reserved keywords though. For instance, Theorem or
Definition stop being a keyword and start to have the same status as
Inductive or CoInductive.
